headline: S ETFs Trail Russell, CRSP Peers in Mid-Cap Race: CFRA
summary: - S&P-linked mid- and small-cap ETFs underperform Russell and Vanguard competitors, says research firm CFRA. - Index methodology differences favor larger-cap names in current market environment. - Market-cap range variations explain performance gaps between competing fund families.
